00:11:18,812 --> 00:11:20,612
Maar beheerste agressie tijdens boksen

250
00:11:20,613 --> 00:11:24,383
je wel relaxt?

251
00:11:24,384 --> 00:11:33,425
Daar wil ik achter komen.

252
00:11:33,426 --> 00:11:35,427
Probeer op m'n gezicht te slaan

253
00:11:35,428 --> 00:11:36,528
Je gezicht?

254
00:11:36,529 --> 00:11:43,435
Zo, ja.

255
